OL,3,CSeven teens convicted of murdering
OL,4,CBailey Atkinson in 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,FFollowing a ten-week trial at
OL,7,FNottingham Crown Court, seven
OL,8,Fteenagers, who were aged between 15
OL,9,Fand 18 at the time of the attack, were
OL,10,Ffound guilty of Mr Atkinson's murder.
OL,11,FThey were Benjamin Wilkes, 18, of
OL,12,FBloxwich, Patrick Brookes, 18, of
OL,13,FWalsall, Sonny Loveridge, 19, of
OL,14,FBloxwich and Ronan McCulloch, 18, of
OL,15,FBloxwich.
OL,17,FThree other teens ` all aged 17 ` were
OL,18,Fconvicted and cannot be named due to
OL,19,Ftheir age.
