OL,3,CSeven teens convicted of murdering
OL,4,CBailey Atkinson in 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,FTwo other defendants also on trial
OL,7,Fwere found not guilty.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Jim Mahon from
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police said the attack
OL,11,Fwas "one of the most shocking" he has
OL,12,Fseen in his time as a police officer.
OL,14,FHe said: "Bailey was unarmed and on a
OL,15,Fnight out walking through Walsall town
OL,16,Fcentre. This was a planned attack, the
OL,17,Fgroup had stolen cars and tried to use
OL,18,Fthe vehicles to seriously injure
OL,19,FBailey.
