OL,3,CSeven teens convicted of murdering
OL,4,CBailey Atkinson in 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,F"They then set upon him in one of the
OL,7,Fmost ferocious attacks I have seen.
OL,8,FFour weapons were used, which included
OL,9,Fa 'rambo' knife and machetes.
OL,11,F"This investigation was complex and
OL,12,Fextremely challenging. We made a total
OL,13,Fof 16 arrests and conducted 12
OL,14,Fmanhunts which led us all around the
OL,15,Fcountry to arrest the suspects. I pay
OL,16,Frespect to Bailey's mother and family,
OL,17,Fwho have had to endure this trial in
OL,18,Fthe same courtroom as his killers.
