OL,3,CSeven teens convicted of murdering
OL,4,CBailey Atkinson in 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,F"Again this highlights the tragic
OL,7,Fconsequences of carrying a knife and
OL,8,Fconflict between groups of young
OL,9,Fpeople. One young man has lost his
OL,10,Flife, while others will face a long
OL,11,Ftime detained in custody and live with
OL,12,Fthe guilt of taking Bailey's life."
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, 31 January 2023, three
OL,15,Fdays after the attack, police arrested
OL,16,Fthree teenagers, two boys aged 15 and
OL,17,Fanother aged 16, at a hotel in north
OL,18,FWales. They were then charged with the
OL,19,Fmurder of Mr Atkinson.
