OL,6,FDays later on 6 February, officers
OL,7,Fdetained two men, aged 19 and 20,
OL,8,Fafter stopping a vehicle in Leamore in
OL,9,FWalsall.
OL,11,F, from an address in Worcester during
OL,12,Fthe early hours of 7 February.
OL,14,FOn 15 February 2023, two more
OL,15,Fteenagers were charged with murder.
OL,16,FThe boys, aged 15 and 17, weren't
OL,17,Fnamed because of their age.
OL,19,FAt that time, the pair were among
OL,20,Feight people charged with murdering Mr
OL,21,FAtkinson.
